'''Neimoidian irregulars''' were a group of [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] soldiers who aided units of [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] infantry in securing and transforming [[Jyvus Space City]] in orbit over [[Duro/Legends|Duro]] into a forward command post for [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]] during the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]]' [[Battle of Duro (Clone Wars)|assault]].

